data.description: HUNTING, FISHING, PRIVACY, it's all here on the beautiful four bedroom two- and one-half bath, with 40 Acres No Covenants, sitting right nextto BLM land on the North side of Keyhole Lake, Property borders BLM land and has some of the best views in the state, custom build home has two bedrooms on the main floor with a large loft sitting area. Off the main floor is a covered wrap around deck for your entertaining of friends or to just sit back and enjoy, large loafing barn with five stalls and tack room 126 x 20 with corrals also has another loafing shed and corral of 20x50, don't miss this opportunity to own this perfect property.
